#. module: bike_leasing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_leasing.catalogue
msgid ""
"Performance and design were the key words during the conception of this "
"super car. No compromises were made to keep the pleasure of driving despite "
"those constraints."
msgstr ""
"Rendiment i disseny van ser les paraules clau durant la creació d'aquest "
"supercotxe. Tot i les limitacions, no es va comprometre cap funcionalitat "
"per garantir que el plaer de conduir es mantingués."

